title: DC One Million
description:
DC One Million, a silver age like story where the Justice League of the 853rd century (1,000,000 months from 1998) travel back in time to pay homage to the original JLA of the late 20th century. Involved is a diplomatic exchange where the original JLA travel forward to the future to exhibit heroic feats in celebration of the meeting.

The most complete DC One Million digital collection I could pull together, in reading order. Young Heroes in Love and Booster Gold 1000000 are missing as they've not been digitised as yet, but every issue integral to the storyline is present.

Also included is material foreshadowing the event, including the last couple of pages of the Rock of Ages storyline as well as the last two pages of JLA 23 (missing until now).

All credit to the original editors of most of this material as well as the person whose supplementary contribution makes this as complete as possible.
